Description:
The optional further dialing sequence     
needed to access addional services (for
example a menu' driven interface)

The personal name of the individual       
(origin to or recipient)

To specify the numeric optional AMIS      
sub-address element as described in
"VPIM Addressing", [RFC3804]

To specify the numeric optional           
extension that identifies a particular
VPIM mailbox as described in "VPIM
Addressing", [RFC3804]

To specify the numeric optional personal  
Distribution list for a particular VPIM
mailbox as described in "VPIM Addressing",
[RFC3804]
